data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home located on a large cul-de-sac lot with a screened in deck and fenced in back yard with new fence gate. This well maintained home updates throughout such as smooth ceilings, freshly painted kitchen and dining areas, beautiful new kitchen sink and fixtures, as well as butcher block countertops adding charm to the heart of the home. Spacious master suite featuring two walk-in closets providing ample storage, space, and comfort. Beautiful countertops in the bathrooms. Downstairs is a full basement featuring a finished den/bonus room as well as a finished office. Roof was replaced at the end of 2020.
